  "title": "PROJECT MANAGER",
  "description": "<p><strong>Responsibilities including but not limited to:</strong><br /></p><ul><li>Conduct client onboarding exercise and complete onboarding checklist, SWOT analysis and gap assessment during the project conception</li><li>Planning with the team, choosing, organizing, and motivating across different vendors</li><li>Overseeing and monitoring all the Campaign progress activities as per the timeline</li><li>Delivering and ensure client satisfaction within budget allocated</li><li>Engage senior stakeholders to discuss and address project issues and risks</li><li>Drive and manage project end to end delivery including requirement, design, testing, deployment</li><li>Taking minutes and ensure proper documentation of client requests to manage delays arising from client or vendor</li><li>Provide timely updates to internal and external stakeholders as per required</li><li>Meet up with clients and conduct presentations whenever there is a need to</li><li>Be on time and reply to clients enquiries whenever necessary</li><li>Ensure all the Digital Marketing Campaign timelines are properly managed</li><li>Works closely with the Digital Marketing team</li><li>Conduct meetings, delicate work and communicate across clients feedback periodically</li></ul><p><strong>Requirements:</strong></p><ul><li>Diploma or Degree in Business Management, Marketing or Marketing Communication</li><li>Pro-active, hardworking, good working attitude, meticulous and results oriented</li><li>Resourceful and problem solver</li><li>Candidates must be able to function in agile work environments</li><li>Excellent analytics skill with strong business acumen</li><li>Excellent interpersonal and communication skills with the ability to translate complex concepts into actionable data and presentation</li><li>Excellent presentation skills that encompass clear, compelling communications tailored to different group of stakeholders</li><li>An advantage to have, Marketing / Digital Marketing background, website development experience</li></ul>",
